    "name": "AoNang Colors Hotel Krabi Aonang Beach",
    "detail": "This hotel is a hidden gem. It is not 5-star but it has everything we needed for a very pleasant stay. The front desk staff are friendly and helpful. Our rooms were large, clean and the bed was comfortable. Another review suggested that the lighting was poor but we did not find it a problem, although the light fitting in the bathroom was a little low. We don't usually eat in hotels but we tried Umbertos and had great food and wine at reasonable prices. As we had driven from Penang, transport around Krabi wasn't a problem but car parking is very difficult along the beachfronts. The hotel is just within walking distance of the beach and there are lots of restaurants along the way. The best bar we found was the Full Moon Bar, which has a great live band, about half way to the beach.",
